**********************************************************************
CLAS - related part **************************************************
**********************************************************************

Basic classes containes global symbol i.e. gCMDaq; 

Creating new class, do not forget:
- "ClassDef(Test, 0)"              - in Test.h
- "ClassImp(Test)"                 - in Test.cxx
- "#pragma link C++ class Test;"   - in LinkDef.h
- "#pragma link C++ global gTest;" - in LinkDef.h if have it in Test.cxx

